294
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:58,790
And sharpen them!

295
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,170
Lu Lingfeng!

296
00:17:55,270 --> 00:17:57,070
Attack it with the cypress wood!

297
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:03,620
