306
00:19:24,550 --> 00:19:26,270
by you youngsters.

307
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:27,630
Come on.

308
00:19:27,950 --> 00:19:29,150
Grandmaster?

309
00:19:29,630 --> 00:19:32,160
