315
00:19:42,470 --> 00:19:43,500
the Memory Pearl,

316
00:19:43,830 --> 00:19:44,830
the Bichen Pearl,

317
00:19:45,070 --> 00:19:47,190
the Shangqing Pearl, the Qingni Pearl,

318
00:19:47,190 --> 00:19:49,470
the Treasure-gathering Pearl, the Evil-dispelling Pearl,

319
00:19:49,470 --> 00:19:52,870
the Snake Pearl, the Charming Pearl, and the Sobering Pearl.

320
00:19:52,990 --> 00:19:54,260
The pearl held by

321
00:19:54,300 --> 00:19:56,450
the White Brow Immortal you worship

322
00:19:56,750 --> 00:19:59,530
is the Sobering Pearl that emits

323
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:00,870
