324
00:20:01,430 --> 00:20:02,960
You don't know that, do you?

325
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:06,570
What happened?

326
00:20:07,090 --> 00:20:08,630
The protective pearl originally held by the immortal

327
00:20:08,630 --> 00:20:09,260
