334
00:20:23,470 --> 00:20:25,930
I was born into a family of treasure hunters.

335
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:28,800
I bought the position of mobile corps commander.

336
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:30,550
Later, our entire family was to be executed

337
00:20:30,550 --> 00:20:31,310
because I hijacked

338
00:20:31,310 --> 00:20:33,070
the tribute from Kang.

339
00:20:34,950 --> 00:20:37,080
Landlady, you heard that, didn't you?

340
00:20:37,110 --> 00:20:37,550
Yes.

341
00:20:38,020 --> 00:20:40,320
The court was indeed in a mess years ago.

342
00:20:40,380 --> 00:20:41,910
But in terms of this matter,

343
00:20:41,990 --> 00:20:43,310
