344
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:45,310
Your brother's death

345
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:47,550
was also caused by him.

346
00:20:52,030 --> 00:20:52,620
And as for

347
00:20:53,430 --> 00:20:55,430
all the veterans here,

348
00:20:55,870 --> 00:20:57,870
they must have been misled by him

349
00:20:58,030 --> 00:20:59,320
into the wrong path.

350
00:21:01,150 --> 00:21:02,430
