356
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:05,910
Dad!

357
00:22:10,150 --> 00:22:10,550
Dad!

358
00:22:12,110 --> 00:22:12,550
Dad.

359
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:14,030
Dad.

360
00:22:18,510 --> 00:22:19,200
Dad!

361
00:22:19,220 --> 00:22:21,680
Don't even think about taking the treasure!

362
00:22:34,230 --> 00:22:35,230
You fake sheriff,

363
00:22:35,310 --> 00:22:36,230
save your strength

364
00:22:36,230 --> 00:22:37,960
for figuring out how to escape.

365
00:23:08,950 --> 00:23:09,750
Sheriff Lu,

366
00:23:11,030 --> 00:23:12,030
you are young

367
00:23:12,630 --> 00:23:13,780
and incredibly skilled in martial arts.

368
00:23:13,780 --> 00:23:14,580
I admire that.

369
00:23:14,910 --> 00:23:15,910
But you're tired.

370
00:23:16,430 --> 00:23:17,150
Moreover,

371
00:23:17,430 --> 00:23:19,230
I have been studying your moves.

372
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:21,910
At this moment, if you think you can defeat me,

373
00:23:22,590 --> 00:23:24,520
you are overestimating yourself.

374
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:30,630
I won't take your life.

375
00:23:32,550 --> 00:23:33,150
Everyone,

376
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:36,710
farewell.

377
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:17,340
Dad.

378
00:24:18,550 --> 00:24:19,310
Dad.

