384
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:36,820
In the forest behind the mountain.

385
00:24:36,820 --> 00:24:37,790
State your name

386
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:38,990
and registered residence,

387
00:24:38,990 --> 00:24:39,950
bind your hands,

388
00:24:40,910 --> 00:24:42,630
