00:26:19,390 --> 00:26:20,520
Carry him upstairs.

415
00:26:31,110 --> 00:26:31,990
Watch out!

416
00:27:00,950 --> 00:27:02,950
Why did you attempt to assassinate Lu Lingfeng?

417
00:27:02,950 --> 00:27:03,990
