418
00:27:13,350 --> 00:27:14,110
Master Long!

419
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:23,870
Fed!

420
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,250
Save him!

421
00:27:37,260 --> 00:27:38,830
Yingtao's injury is not severe.

422
00:27:38,830 --> 00:27:40,030
Chicken Fed said a few days of rest

423
00:27:40,030 --> 00:27:40,830
