433
00:27:59,030 --> 00:27:59,950
Yes, Brother.

434
00:28:00,320 --> 00:28:01,350
Tell him.

435
00:28:09,750 --> 00:28:11,510
This gold was found

436
00:28:11,950 --> 00:28:13,190
on Jia Buli.

437
00:28:16,350 --> 00:28:18,440
This document

438
00:28:18,470 --> 00:28:19,670
was found on Lan Juzi.

439
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:23,950
The gold

440
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:26,190
and the deposit

441
00:28:26,210 --> 00:28:27,080
on the document

442
00:28:27,350 --> 00:28:28,350
match perfectly.

443
00:28:28,470 --> 00:28:29,230
I think

444
00:28:29,430 --> 00:28:30,390
these two

445
00:28:30,430 --> 00:28:31,560
are bounty hunters.

446
00:28:31,710 --> 00:28:33,350
What are bounty hunters?

447
00:28:34,630 --> 00:28:35,590
They are people who take money

448
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:36,270
to kill

449
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:37,850
others' enemies.

450
00:28:39,230 --> 00:28:40,670
But I have no enemies

451
00:28:44,430 --> 00:28:45,430
Maybe

452
00:28:45,990 --> 00:28:47,920
