00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:50,150
This letter paper

454
00:28:50,630 --> 00:28:52,230
is not used by common people.

455
00:29:02,030 --> 00:29:03,030
It's exclusively

456
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:06,190
for the Eastern Palace.

457
00:29:07,870 --> 00:29:10,720
Now that the new emperor has ascended the throne,

458
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:12,230
former items from the Eastern Palace

459
00:29:12,230 --> 00:29:13,790
could have ended up among the common people

460
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:16,350
and been stolen by ill-intentioned individuals.

461
00:29:16,350 --> 00:29:17,480
Don't overthink it.

462
00:29:26,260 --> 00:29:27,520
If he wanted to kill me,

463
00:29:29,590 --> 00:29:31,720
why didn't he issue a decree directly?

464
00:29:36,700 --> 00:29:37,960
-Lu Lingfeng!
-Xijun!

465
00:29:40,260 --> 00:29:42,040
Let him be alone for a while.

466
00:29:51,250 --> 00:29:58,300
[Mo's Inn]

467
00:30:02,950 --> 00:30:04,580
The bodies of the murdered construction workers

468
00:30:04,580 --> 00:30:06,150
