475
00:30:15,310 --> 00:30:16,310
Hurry up.

476
00:30:17,030 --> 00:30:17,510
Be good.

477
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:20,710
Sheriff Jiang,

478
00:30:20,990 --> 00:30:21,710
This is...

479
00:30:22,030 --> 00:30:23,500
the so-called...

480
00:30:23,630 --> 00:30:25,870
Treasure Hunting Grandmaster's donkey.

481
00:30:25,870 --> 00:30:27,800
