00:30:37,350 --> 00:30:37,880
Alright.

486
00:30:38,310 --> 00:30:39,390
I'll make the decision.

487
00:30:39,390 --> 00:30:40,050
It's yours.

488
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:42,390
Thank you.

489
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:45,780
I also owe you thanks, Physician Fei,

490
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,210
