494
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,990
From now on, we are family.

495
00:30:58,100 --> 00:31:01,650
[Three days later]

496
00:31:02,390 --> 00:31:03,510
In this remote inn,

497
00:31:04,170 --> 00:31:06,380
it is my great honor

498
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:09,230
to have met all of you.

499
00:31:10,510 --> 00:31:11,110
Mr. Lu,

500
00:31:11,470 --> 00:31:12,790
although you have been demoted to Yunding,

501
00:31:12,790 --> 00:31:13,990
I believe that the day

502
00:31:14,430 --> 00:31:16,490
when the bad times are over will come.

503
00:31:16,950 --> 00:31:18,550
Mr. Su, the same goes for you.

504
00:31:19,590 --> 00:31:20,230
I will be

505
00:31:20,870 --> 00:31:21,730
in Shen County,

506
00:31:22,260 --> 00:31:23,790
waiting for your good news.

507
00:31:24,630 --> 00:31:25,030
Here.

508
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:27,200
A toast to everyone.

509
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:38,830
Mr. Lu,

510
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:40,510
I have one more favor

511
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:41,510
