520
00:31:58,590 --> 00:31:59,050
Well...

521
00:32:00,310 --> 00:32:02,110
Men from the Lu family of Fanyang

522
00:32:02,180 --> 00:32:04,430
are all gentlemen,

523
00:32:04,710 --> 00:32:05,790
known for valuing trust

524
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:07,050
and keeping promises.

525
00:32:07,340 --> 00:32:08,670
Sheriff Jiang

526
00:32:08,750 --> 00:32:10,870
