528
00:32:14,830 --> 00:32:15,310
Indeed.

529
00:32:18,580 --> 00:32:19,310
In that case,

530
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:20,390
I will surely

531
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:22,540
accomplish this mission.

532
00:32:26,110 --> 00:32:26,750
Thank you.

533
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:37,480
