568
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:50,320
Fei Yingjun,

569
00:35:52,050 --> 00:35:53,990
as the newly appointed sheriff of Yunding in the Tang Dynasty,

570
00:35:53,990 --> 00:35:55,660
