582
00:36:18,950 --> 00:36:20,470
while freely wandering in the wilderness.

583
00:36:20,470 --> 00:36:22,430
I'm the most suitable person

584
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:24,100
to release Long Tai.

585
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:26,640
You admitted it so quickly.

586
00:36:28,180 --> 00:36:29,380
This is not the court.

587
00:36:29,590 --> 00:36:30,410
Yes, I let him go.

588
00:36:30,410 --> 00:36:32,190
