591
00:36:35,580 --> 00:36:37,870
Long Tai has good martial arts skills

592
00:36:37,930 --> 00:36:39,590
and a strong sense of justice.

593
00:36:39,990 --> 00:36:42,270
May he be on the right path in the future,

594
00:36:42,750 --> 00:36:44,390
becoming a hero, not a thief.

595
00:36:45,430 --> 00:36:46,230
Fei Yingjun,

596
