607
00:37:12,790 --> 00:37:13,720
if I hand it over,

608
00:37:14,150 --> 00:37:15,560
it will be passed from one officer to another.

609
00:37:15,560 --> 00:37:16,150
It'll definitely end up in the hands

610
00:37:16,150 --> 00:37:17,670
of some corrupt official.

611
00:37:19,110 --> 00:37:20,510
So, it's better

612
00:37:20,530 --> 00:37:21,690
for me to keep it.

613
00:37:23,790 --> 00:37:24,360
Brother,

614
00:37:24,730 --> 00:37:26,720
this sobering pearl is unclaimed,

615
00:37:27,510 --> 00:37:30,230
and Chicken Fed loves drinking like his life depends on it.

616
00:37:30,230 --> 00:37:31,230
So if he has it,

617
00:37:31,410 --> 00:37:33,110
it can be considered putting it to good use.

618
00:37:33,110 --> 00:37:33,710
Well said.

619
00:37:34,260 --> 00:37:35,260
Xijun has a point.

620
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:36,480
Now, Uncle Fed

621
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:37,960
will never make mistakes due to being drunk again.

622
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:38,800
That's right

623
00:37:39,670 --> 00:37:40,590
