my spear.

628
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:47,430
Wasn't it just that one time?

629
00:37:47,430 --> 00:37:47,800
You

630
00:37:48,430 --> 00:37:50,030
are the great general of the Lu family of Fanyang.

631
00:37:50,030 --> 00:37:51,320
Don't be so petty,

632
00:37:52,070 --> 00:37:54,330
and won't let this little slip of mine go.

633
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:55,730
Let's go. Let's go.

634
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:28,230
Don't worry.

635
00:38:28,850 --> 00:38:30,000
The two of us

636
00:38:30,030 --> 00:38:32,030
are the best bounty hunters

637
00:38:32,870 --> 00:38:34,130
and have never failed.

638
00:38:35,830 --> 00:38:37,430
I have finished the documents.

639
00:38:37,430 --> 00:38:39,490
If we fail to take Lu Lingfeng's life,

640
00:38:39,680 --> 00:38:41,570
we will offer our lives instead.

641
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:48,510
There can't really be such a person, right?

642
00:39:48,510 --> 00:39:49,550
What kind of person?

643
00:39:49,550 --> 00:39:50,750
My master once told me

644
00:39:50,910 --> 00:39:52,930
that in this world, there are so-called cultivators

645
00:39:52,930 --> 00:39:54,510
who have mastered the art of divine walking.

646
00:39:54,510 --> 00:39:55,990
They can walk as fast as flying.

647
00:39:55,990 --> 00:39:57,350
He specifically mentioned

648
00:39:57,350 --> 00:39:58,700
that by using a certain technique

649
00:39:58,700 --> 00:40:00,860
to dredge the meridians and improve blood flow inside the body,

650
00:40:00,860 --> 00:40:01,660
one can achieve

651
00:40:01,660 --> 00:40:03,310
the effect of feeling as light as a swallow.

652
00:40:03,310 --> 00:40:05,500
So they can leave in the morning and arrive at their destination in the evening.

653
00:40:05,500 --> 00:40:07,350
If one temporarily removes their kneecaps,

654
00:40:07,350 --> 00:40:09,150
then they can travel 800 li a day.

655
00:40:10,790 --> 00:40:13,920
One can still walk after having one's kneecaps removed?

656
00:40:16,060 --> 00:40:16,710
Yeah.

657
00:40:17,270 --> 00:40:18,570
It's possible for a person

658
00:40:18,570 --> 00:40:20,230
to run fast through practice.

659
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:22,030
But traveling 800 li a day

660
00:40:22,030 --> 00:40:23,090
without kneecaps?

661
00:40:23,630 --> 00:40:24,690
I don't believe it.

662
00:40:25,910 --> 00:40:26,470
Yingtao,

663
00:40:26,950 --> 00:40:28,990
