664
00:40:28,990 --> 00:40:31,250
But this kind of story is indeed absurd.

665
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:33,520
What do you think, Fed?

666
00:40:35,770 --> 00:40:38,450
I think it must hurt.

667
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:39,960
Of course, it will hurt.

668
00:40:41,110 --> 00:40:42,550
If there was another way,

669
00:40:43,510 --> 00:40:44,840
I wouldn't be like this.

670
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:50,270
Are you sick?

671
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:51,390
No,

672
00:40:51,910 --> 00:40:53,270
what I mean is

673
00:40:53,300 --> 00:40:54,980
that I can treat you.

674
00:40:55,830 --> 00:40:56,290
No need.

675
00:40:56,750 --> 00:40:57,270
No need.

676
00:40:58,230 --> 00:40:59,150
Yu Di's illness

677
00:40:59,390 --> 00:41:01,390
