678
00:41:01,630 --> 00:41:02,990
Your name is Yu Di, like Yu Di Emperor?

679
00:41:02,990 --> 00:41:04,310
You've got nerve.

680
00:41:04,710 --> 00:41:05,640
Using this name,

681
00:41:05,670 --> 00:41:08,630
