682
00:41:08,630 --> 00:41:09,510
My name

683
00:41:09,590 --> 00:41:11,270
is different from his name.

684
00:41:10,030 --> 00:41:13,140
[Liu Yu Di]

685
00:41:12,150 --> 00:41:13,070
The same word

686
00:41:13,270 --> 00:41:15,070
but with different characters.

687
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:17,830
Well...

688
00:41:18,300 --> 00:41:18,760
Well...

689
00:41:19,510 --> 00:41:21,190
What illness do you actually have?

690
00:41:21,190 --> 00:41:21,870
Yes.

691
00:41:22,070 --> 00:41:22,790
Tell us.

692
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:24,890
Uncle Fed is not an ordinary doctor.

693
00:41:24,890 --> 00:41:26,690
He's a miracle-working doctor.

694
00:41:27,270 --> 00:41:28,110
Forget it.

695
00:41:28,680 --> 00:41:30,160
I won't trouble you anymore.

696
00:41:30,160 --> 00:41:30,720
Sir...

697
00:41:32,900 --> 00:41:33,930
Old miracle doctor,

698
00:41:33,930 --> 00:41:35,060
thank you very much.

699
00:41:36,710 --> 00:41:37,510
You...

700
00:41:37,870 --> 00:41:39,230
are quite polite.

701
00:41:39,840 --> 00:41:41,770
I see you don't have a horse either.

702
00:41:41,820 --> 00:41:42,610
Why don't you travel with us?

703
00:41:42,610 --> 00:41:43,170
No need.

704
00:41:43,510 --> 00:41:43,990
No need.

705
00:41:44,770 --> 00:41:45,430
Besides,

706
00:41:46,030 --> 00:41:47,760
we may not be going the same way.

707
00:41:47,870 --> 00:41:48,830
Have a safe journey, everyone.

708
00:41:48,830 --> 00:41:49,470
Alright.

709
00:41:50,310 --> 00:41:51,830
Let's not disturb him anymore.

710
00:41:51,830 --> 00:41:53,290
We need to hurry on our way.

711
00:41:53,590 --> 00:41:54,050
Let's go

712
00:41:58,490 --> 00:41:59,110
I...

713
00:42:22,250 --> 00:42:23,710
The great river surges on.

714
00:42:23,850 --> 00:42:24,980
It seems much wider

715
00:42:24,990 --> 00:42:26,390
than described in books.

716
00:42:29,070 --> 00:42:30,150
It's still early.

717
00:42:30,630 --> 00:42:32,320
How come there's no ferry boat?

718
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:33,470
Let's walk along the river

719
00:42:33,470 --> 00:42:34,750
