728
00:42:48,970 --> 00:42:50,370
Drinking is all you know.

729
00:42:50,430 --> 00:42:51,160
So what then?

730
00:42:51,430 --> 00:42:52,850
Do I have to get that Boat Officer

731
00:42:52,850 --> 00:42:54,850
