740
00:43:45,500 --> 00:43:47,710
If you don't want to take the boat at night,

741
00:43:47,710 --> 00:43:49,040
you can stay here for now

742
00:43:49,470 --> 00:43:50,950
and leave in the morning.

743
00:43:51,430 --> 00:43:52,560
If you are in a hurry,

744
00:43:54,830 --> 00:43:56,290
